import React from 'react'
import { Container, DesktopIcons, DesktopIconsContainer, DishType, SpicyLogo, TypeDiv, VeganLogo, VegitarianLogo } from './StyleSignatures'

export default function DesktopSignatureDishOf() {
  return (
    <DesktopIconsContainer>
       <DishType>THE MEANING OF OUR ICONS: </DishType>
       <DesktopIcons>
        <TypeDiv>
            <SpicyLogo/>
            <DishType>Spicy</DishType>
        </TypeDiv>

        <TypeDiv>
            <VegitarianLogo/>
            <DishType>Vegitarian</DishType>
        </TypeDiv>

        <TypeDiv>
            <VeganLogo/>
            <DishType>Vegan</DishType>
        </TypeDiv> 
        </DesktopIcons>
    </DesktopIconsContainer>

  )
}
